---
title: Super-Speedy Beef Lo Mein with Garlic Chili Oil & Sesame Seeds
description: You’ll be digging into this comforting, fully loaded noodle bowl in less time than it would take to order takeout! Tender, chewy noodles are tossed with savory ground beef and crisp-tender cabbage and carrots, then coated with an umami-rich sweet soy glaze. It’s all sprinkled with scallions, drizzled with homemade chili-garlic oil for a kick, and finished with a shower of nutty sesame seeds for crunch. Get ready to curl up in your favorite spot with a delicious bowl of lo mein straight from your kitchen in just 15 minutes!
